iao_definition: ['Any method where a sample mixture is first separated by gas chromatography then ionised and characterised according to mass-to-charge ratio and relative abundance.']
label: ['gas chromatography-mass spectrometry']
oio_exact_synonym: ['gas chromatography mass spectrometry', 'gas chromatography mass spectroscopy', 'gas chromatography with mass spectrometric detection', 'gas chromatography-mass spectroscopy', 'gas chromatography/mass spectrometry', 'GC MS', 'GC-MS', 'GC/MS', 'GCMS']

iao_definition: ['Albumen is the clear liquid contained within an egg and consists of water and proteins, among which are ovomucin and ovomucoid. It protects the egg yolk and provides additional nutrition for the growth of the embryo.']
label: ['albumen']

iao_definition: ['An aromatic ketone that is acetophenone in which one of the ortho hydrogens of the phenyl group has been replaced by an amino group.']
label: ['o-aminoacetophenone']

iao_definition: ['The role played by a substance in enhancing the appearance or odour of the human body; a name given to the substance itself or to a component of it.']

iao_definition: ['The process of existence without reproduction of a pathogen of a particular biological taxon in or on some material entity or the process of reproduction of a pathogen in or on a material entity that is not an organism.']
rdf_comment: ['the preferred term is biological contamination to distinguish from things like radiological contamination, contamination of the Gulf of Mexico with oil, the contamination of air with pollution, etc.']
label: ['contamination']
